## **WHAT HAPPENED BEHIND THE SCENES**

### **System Tracking:**

**From Passive Exercises:**

- ✅ All 5 root words comprehended in multiple contexts
- ✅ Nuance between "back" (financial vs. emotional) noticed
- ✅ "Burn through" understood with different objects (money, time, budget)
- ✅ "Pull off" vs. "take off" distinguished correctly
- ✅ "Pivot" understood in both business and personal contexts

**Child Elements Encountered (First Time):**

- "back someone on something" (appeared in Reading 1)
- "burn through time" (appeared in Reading 1)
- These are now added to Jenny's vocab bank
- Their SRS cycle starts today
- Next appearance: in 3 days, integrated into different content

**From Active Exercises:**

- ✅ All 5 phrases produced naturally in appropriate contexts
- ✅ Register correctly adjusted (professional vs. casual)
- ✅ No awkward forced usage
- ✅ Phrases served communicative goals (not just vocabulary display)

**Updated SRS Schedule:**

- Original 5 words: Next review in 3 days (Day 4)
- 2 new child elements: Will appear in Day 3 review content
- If Jenny succeeds again on Day 4, interval increases to 7 days

